npm init -y
npm install --save-dev @types/node
docker-compose up -d #starts Hoverfly + proxy controller
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/v1/chat/completions -d "{\"url\":\"https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1\"}" #POST request to the proxy controller with data = actual endpoint

Aliter:
If not using Docker then start the proxy controller and hoverfly separately:
start hoverfly by refering to https://docs.hoverfly.io/en/latest/pages/introduction/gettingstarted.html
start the proxy controller: node Myserver.js (localhost:3000)


curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/v1/chat/completions -d "{\"url\":\"https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions\",\"model\": \"gpt-3.5-turbo\", \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello!\"}]}"

